snippet.title: Scott's Treasures: Akira - Incomplete / Unreleased Nintendo Game Boy Prototype Game
snippet.description:
This game was long thought lost, only for four unfinished builds of it to turn up in 2016. Here's a look.

There's been much claimed online about these, which I'll call faux "Contri-versies" created and spread by people without 99.9 percent of the information they need to make any such claims. 

I've written about the real story many times but few want to listen. If you want to know the truth of the matter, feel free to email me or comment below.
